channel.title: CacheDownloader for PI/DSPK
channel.description: Well, I've recently been wanting to upload my cache so the client download is quite a bit smaller. I was wondering if uppit and mediafire worked for this? My internet isn't near good enough to use dropbox. Any other sites that work?

item.description:

Pretty sure you can use all file hosting sites, oh and btw is your internet powered by a hamster?

And no, this internet is temporary until we can afford better net. We recently made home renovations so I’m on an Verizon air-card. 75kb/s upload speed ftl.
